            <p>My experience spans a wide range of technologies, providing me with a solid foundation in network architecture, system administration, identity and access management, automation, and secure infrastructure deployment. I am well-versed in tools and concepts such as virtual networking, firewalls, routing and switching, virtualization, and cloud services including Azure Virtual Networks, Virtual Machines, and App Services.</p>

            <p>In addition to my technical background, I bring valuable experience managing banking infrastructure within a New York-based institution operating across seven branches. In this role, I was responsible for maintaining and optimizing a multi-site network environment, supporting secure inter-branch connectivity, managing centralized systems, and ensuring high availability and compliance within a regulated financial setting.</p>

            <p>Beyond technical expertise, I place a strong emphasis on teamwork, communication, and adaptability. I have consistently sought opportunities to collaborate with cross-functional teams, recognizing the value of diverse perspectives in solving complex problems.</p>

            <a href="/shared/docs/resume.pdf" class="resume-cta">Download My Resume</a>
